1. *Mu* je baka dala neki poklon. (His/Her grandmother gave him/her a present.) 
2. Pošalji mi *mu* poruku. (Send him a message.)
3. Ja sam zahvalan *mu* za pomoć. (I am grateful to him for his help.)
4. *Mu* je stan iznajmljen. (His/Her apartment has been rented.)
5. On je dao *mu* knjigu. (He gave him/her a book.)
6. Ona se nada da će *mu* biti potrebna. (She hopes it will be useful for him/her.)